CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Strata Critical Medical provides time critical logistics solutions and specialized medical services to healthcare providers across the United States, strategically expanding its portfolio of services through acquisition and organic growth. Strata's subsidiary, Trinity Medical Solutions, is an industry leader in air and ground transportation of human organs for transplant, leveraging Strata's asset-light platform to reliably and efficiently deliver logistics solutions to its customers across the United States.
